Interface RuleInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface RuleInfo
extends java.io.Serializable
    DELETEME_LATER: [This code has been imported from BIUTEE, with (no modifications)] Implementations of this interface hold the additional information pertinent to a LexicalRule of that implementation, but not covered by the fields of LexicalRule, for instance the synsets of a wordnet rule, or the extraction type of a wikipedia rule.

    Implementations must be immutable, and implement equals() and hasCode()!
